name: 劳拉·里德
introduction: Laura Reid is an Australian actress who also has experience in other areas of the arts such as music and dance. Laura has a Bachelor of Arts in Contemporary and Applied Theatre Awards Major in Advanced Theatre from Griffith University. Laura has a variety of film and TV credits and has performed in numerous musical and contemporary theatre productions. She has also trained extensively in Los Angles USA and in Australia. As of 2020, she is coached by Howard Fine. Laura is best known for her role of Daisy Girl in Baz Luhrmanns Elvis (2022) and Linda in Peacocks Joe vs. Carole (2022).
